'''天使城堡''' （{{lang-gr|Αγγελόκαστρο }}，Angelokastro）是[[希腊|希腊]][[科孚岛|科孚岛]]上一个[[拜占庭|拜占庭]][[城堡|城堡]]，<ref name=Stamatopoulos/><ref name="Kordōsēs1981">{{cite book|authors=Michaēl S. Kordōsēs (Μιχαήλ Κορδώσης Καθηγητής Ιστορικής Γεωγραφίας, Πανεπιστήμιο Ιωαννίνων)|title=Symvolē stēn historia kai topographia tēs periochēs Korinthou stous mesous chronous|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=kmE_AQAAIAAJ&q=%CE%92%CF%85%CE%B6%CE%B1%CE%BD%CF%84%CE%B9%CE%BD%CE%BF+%CE%91%CE%B3%CE%B3%CE%B5%CE%BB%CF%8C%CE%BA%CE%B1%CF%83%CF%84%CF%81%CE%BF&dq=%CE%92%CF%85%CE%B6%CE%B1%CE%BD%CF%84%CE%B9%CE%BD%CE%BF+%CE%91%CE%B3%CE%B3%CE%B5%CE%BB%CF%8C%CE%BA%CE%B1%CF%83%CF%84%CF%81%CE%BF&hl=en&sa=X&ei=9pQ6UsruMpOWyAG2ioBI&ved=0CFIQ6AEwBg|accessdate=2013-09-19|year=1981|publisher=Vivliopōleio D.N. Karavia|page=140|quote=|archive-date=2014-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627172801/http://books.google.com/books?id=kmE_AQAAIAAJ&q=%CE%92%CF%85%CE%B6%CE%B1%CE%BD%CF%84%CE%B9%CE%BD%CE%BF+%CE%91%CE%B3%CE%B3%CE%B5%CE%BB%CF%8C%CE%BA%CE%B1%CF%83%CF%84%CF%81%CE%BF&dq=%CE%92%CF%85%CE%B6%CE%B1%CE%BD%CF%84%CE%B9%CE%BD%CE%BF+%CE%91%CE%B3%CE%B3%CE%B5%CE%BB%CF%8C%CE%BA%CE%B1%CF%83%CF%84%CF%81%CE%BF&hl=en&sa=X&ei=9pQ6UsruMpOWyAG2ioBI&ved=0CFIQ6AEwBg|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它位于科孚岛西北海岸，海边高达{{convert|1000|ft|0|abbr=on}}的陡峭的山崖上方，为全岛海岸线最高峰的顶部。<ref name=Stamatopoulos>{{cite book|last=Stamatopoulos|first=Nondas|title=Old Corfu: history and culture|year=1993|publisher=N. Stamatopoulos|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=6m0-AQAAIAAJ&q=Angelocastro&dq=Angelocastro&hl=en&ei=TJuwTvzvCur00gHmhNy-AQ&sa=X&oi|edition=3|quote=|access-date=2017-03-24|archive-date=2018-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181006235213/https://books.google.ca/books?id=6m0-AQAAIAAJ&q=Angelocastro&dq=Angelocastro&hl=en&ei=TJuwTvzvCur00gHmhNy-AQ&sa=X&oi|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BowmanKerasiotis2012">{{cite book|author1=John S. Bowman|author2=Peter Kerasiotis|author3=Sherry Marker|title=Frommer's Greece|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2C9QJ5Ie0kAC&pg=PA567|accessdate=2013-02-11|date=2012-01-10|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=978-1-118-20577-8|page=567|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729171439/https://books.google.com/books?id=2C9QJ5Ie0kAC&pg=PA567|dead-url=no}}</ref>

天使城堡是科孚岛最重要的防御工事之一，控制[[亚得里亚海|亚得里亚海]]南部的战略制高点。

天使城堡形成一个防御三角形 与Gardiki 城堡和卡西奥皮城堡, 涵盖科孚岛南、西北和东北三面的防御。
